<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Shoes Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Your go-to destination for the latest in footwear fashion!</p>
    </header>

    <section class="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At ShoeStyle, we believe that every step you take should be in style and comfort. Our mission is to provide
            high-quality footwear that combines fashion, comfort, and affordability.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="history">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2020, ShoeStyle started as a small store with a simple goal: to provide stylish and affordable
            shoes to everyone. Over the years, we have expanded our collection and established a loyal customer base.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="team">
        <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
        <div class="team-member" onclick="showDetails('john')">
            <h3>John Doe</h3>
            <p>CEO & Founder</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member" onclick="showDetails('jane')">
            <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
            <p>Head Designer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member" onclick="showDetails('alex')">
            <h3>Alex Johnson</h3>
            <p>Marketing Manager</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="details" class="details">
        <h2>Team Member Details</h2>
        <p id="detail-info"></p>
        <button onclick="closeDetails()">Close</button>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 ShoeStyle. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
</body>

</html>